 />\n灣仔、銅鑼灣、天后、炮台山: 維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌、太古、西灣河、筲箕灣: 沿海旁<br />\n小西灣、杏花邨、柴灣: 柴灣公園<br />\n鑽石山、黃大仙: 黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍灣、牛頭角、觀塘: 觀塘海濱公園<br />\n大圍、沙田、馬鞍山 : 沙田百步梯<br />\n元朗、天水圍: 天水園公園<br />\n屯門: 屯門公園<br />\n南區: 鴨利洲風之塔公園<br />\n<br />\n仲有獅子山同山頂人鏈!"},{"pid":"afb0274fc2c81321b38d1f30f25c37c23c6e9a55","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/hkdse2020tg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkdse2020tg&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QbccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=a13e2c47\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkdse2020tg</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7d03b28842d21697463c196f6f5833a7ab412b","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"daf5a79b07ba50f44b55612c5b95bdb3ef783044","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97abb23d4d233c786593224a9ab26a287fd2b01","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ce7f4eba866c9d3304604101f1d8f2cbcd89d6","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ab1caa2ab3d045ea8c6800242bb84c9bad1a9513","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59df072a5f3eb9cd6d036f39e7c8a68d3a56396a","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"930b04e9173e6eac1d90ff81a4fa16bf7b40fb3c","tid":1565622,"uid":49042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite